8. Boundary Criteriaï½œHow to Tell Tasking vs. Non-Tasking

This section clarifies what counts as tasking and
prevents confusion with safe techniques like emotional concretization.

8.1 What Counts as Tasking (EW-05 Prohibited)

Any one of the following appearing = tasking.

(1) Goal-directed language

â€œTo feel better, you canâ€¦â€

â€œTry describing it, it will help you adjust.â€

â€œWhat you need to do now isâ€¦â€

â†’ Treats emotion as something that must be fixed.

